      "raw_text": "Mayor N. S. Pratt is sanguine\nthat union depot will be\nbuilt. He thinks. the outlook\nIs brighter now than at any\nprevious period since the agita-\nton for the joint passenger\nterminal began.\n\n\n\"The union depot is COMING\"\nhe said to The Press. \"You\ncannot stop it now, and | look\nfor all the different interests\nto get together on the PROPOSE\nticn soon.\""
